

=Bio=

Beatriz García has studied History and Anthropology. Her work is developed around public policies, specially in health and education; migrations and micropolitics; and the production of subjectivity. She is part of the [[Traficantes de Sueños]] project as editor, proofreader and coordinator of Nociones Comunes, a formation and knowledge production space.


